    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个权限系统设计一个类图，核心是四个实体：User、Role、Permission，还有Team。Team作为隔离维度，每个团队有自己的角色和权限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Role",
        "Permission",
        "Team"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Team是隔离边界。那User和Role之间是多对多关系吗？一个用户可以有多个角色，一个角色也可以分配给多个用户？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Role"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，多对多。Role和Permission也是多对多，角色拥有权限。另外User也可以直接拥有Permission，不走角色，这是直接授权的场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Role",
        "Permission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这四个类画出来，User、Role、Permission、Team，然后建立多对多关联。Role到Permission标为\"has\"，User到Role也是\"has\"，User到Permission同样\"has\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Role",
        "Permission",
        "Team"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
